{"tid":2192120,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿嬌大陸拍戲酒店房出意外 頭部嚴重受傷需即時送醫","createTime":"2020-09-07T02:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T07:01:20.000Z","uid":48631,"like":36,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee6f8bc36a6e1cc686462598becff1af936145e","tid":2192120,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:24:37.000Z","msg":"今天零晨兩點多，鐘欣潼（阿嬌）在中國廈門下榻的酒店房間內發生意外，頭部嚴重受傷，她第一時間通知閨密容祖兒及經理人霍汶希。因為傷勢嚴重，阿嬌已即時送往廈門大學第一附屬醫院，身在北京的Mani和容祖兒，亦馬上乘北京往廈門的第一班飛機去協助阿嬌。<br />\n<br />\n阿嬌原定今晨六點拍攝最後一場戲，不想耽誤戲組的阿嬌，受傷後一度堅持要繼續前往劇組拍晨戲，但因傷勢不輕需留醫院觀察，經理人霍汶希不允許她繼續開工。<br />\n<br />\n據知，Mani及祖兒已抵醫院了解情況，《蘋果》今早致電Mani，她未有接聽電話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200907/QBXDBL73VVDDPLVGO3M4IFKWQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200907%2FQBXDBL73VVDDPLVGO3M4IFKWQI%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=99d62591\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200907%2FQBXDBL73VVDDPLVGO3M4IFKWQI%2F&h=f813f09c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200907/QBXDBL73VVDDPLVGO3M4IFKWQI/</a>"},{"pid":"93defc5ebfcde9c1da77079cb6dff502f20a83dc","tid":2192120,"uid":213812,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"撞親個頭之後份人可能無再咁戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08dae4fbae73e583ed67ad0668fc0d70349ae005","tid":2192120,"uid":20870,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:25:55.000Z","msg":"仲有能力開工？"},{"pid":"ebe648a002fc45f445815ed318c5a0c3868b1cc0","tid":2192120,"uid":161945,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:26:05.000Z","msg":"酒店房可以有咩意外？<br />\n唔係廁所太滑呀？"},{"pid":"00f1e671742d5b09b62a7863fb47da480775a21f","tid":2192120,"uid":161945,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:26:52.000Z","msg":"定係唔肯幫大陸佬含<br />\n所以俾人